{"question":"\r\n<div class='specificatio'>\r\n<p><spa style=\"fot-family: times ew oma,times; fot-size: medium;\">Let&bsp; \\(f(x) = {\\si ^3}x + {\\cos ^3}x\\ta x,\\fac{\\pi }{2} &lt; x &lt; \\pi \\) .<spa><p>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<div class='questio' style='paddig-left: 20px; paddig-ight: 20px;'>\r\n<p><spa style=\"fot-family: times ew oma,times; fot-size: medium;\">Show that \\(f(x) = \\si x\\) .<spa><p>\r\n<div class='maks'>[2]<div>\r\n<div class='questio_pat_label'>a.<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class='questio' style='paddig-left: 20px; paddig-ight: 20px;'>\r\n<p alig=\"LEFT\"><spa style=\"fot-family: times ew oma,times; fot-size: medium;\">Let \\(\\si x = \\fac{2}{3}\\) <spa><spa style=\"fot-family: times ew oma,times; fot-size: medium;\">. Show that \\(f(2x) = - \\fac{{4\\sqt 5 }}{9}\\)<spa><spa style=\"fot-family: times ew oma,times; fot-size: medium;\"> .<spa><p>\r\n<div class='maks'>[5]<div>\r\n<div class='questio_pat_label'>b.<div>\r\n<div>\r\n","markschems":"\r\n<div class='question' style='padding-left: 20px;'>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;\">changing \\(\\tan x\\)&nbsp;into \\(\\frac{{\\sin x}}{{\\cos x}}\\)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong><em>A1</em> </strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;\">e.g. \\({\\sin ^3}x + {\\cos ^3}x\\frac{{\\sin x}}{{\\cos x}}\\)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;\">simplifying&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1 </strong></em></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;\">e.g \\(\\sin x({\\sin ^2}x + {\\cos ^2}x)\\) , \\({\\sin ^3}x + \\sin x - {\\sin ^3}x\\)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;\">\\(f(x) = \\sin x\\)&nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>AG &nbsp; &nbsp; N0</strong> </em></span></p>\r\n<p><em><strong><span style=\"font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;\">[2 marks]</span></